I knew something would turn up.
Where's that dress for Tessie?

1745
01:51:11,832 --> 01:51:14,502
It'll work perfect for you.
Well, get into your makeup.

1746
01:51:14,710 --> 01:51:16,750
There isn't much time.

1747
