No, I'll be dead.

1933
02:08:22,904 --> 02:08:24,994
Renee, would you take this tray
out of here?

1934
02:08:25,198 --> 02:08:27,408
- I'll do it.
- Mother, please.

1935
02:08:27,617 --> 02:08:29,987
And bring my press agent in
as soon as he comes.

1936
